div.p:
Furthermore, Y.P.K. Śrī Jayaparameśvaravarmadeva, the P.P.K., offered to Yām̃ Pu Nagara and the Holy Form in this year of the Śaka king 1155:
             rice-field at Kumvyām̃l, one unit. In this place, the rice-field of great abundance; 400 jāk. Khmers who are given to this domain: 10 men and women;
            this rice-field vanūk at Dharmmathateḥ: 1800 jāk; this rice-field vanūk at Pu Auk: 1500 jāk; Khmers, Cams, Chinese (?), Siamese, Paganese: 45 men and women.
